<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Admin Gate - Cipher Lounge</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-black text-white flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen">
  <form action="/admin/unlock" method="POST" class="bg-white/5 border border-green-400/30 p-8 rounded-xl w-full max-w-md shadow-xl space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400 text-center">🔐 Admin Access</h1>
    
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm text-center">
      To enter the control room, solve the cipher...
    </p>
    <p>"Speak backwards and you may pass: emanym"</p>
    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-white">Enter Passphrase</label>
    <input 
      type="password"
      name="captcha"
      class="mt-1 w-full px-4 py-2 bg-black/40 border border-white/20 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-400"
      placeholder="••••••••••"
      required
    />

    <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-400 transition font-bold py-2 rounded-lg">
      Enter
    </button>
  </form>
</body>
</html>
